{"tid":1172751,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港不是寒蟬效應　是沒有言論自由　言論自由是免代價、免恐懼","createTime":"2019-05-26T15:51:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-27T03:11:07.000Z","uid":47714,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"4db158c92a140ae5fb804e0c3335b806a85254c6","tid":1172751,"uid":47714,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T15:51:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://twitter.com/LungZenoOpen/status/1132179898590621696\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLungZenoOpen%2Fstatus%2F1132179898590621696&d=N%2B9SyAXHNe8JODsndO18Bbc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=a6791439\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FLungZenoOpen%2Fstatus%2F1132179898590621696&h=5f8d9496\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/LungZenoOpen/status/1132179898590621696</a><br />\n<br />\n香港人喜歡自由，但另一方面，很多香港人不會冒風險。張堅庭導演過去97前會出品政治諷刺笑片、表姐你好嘢系列，但他說了他不是烈士，現在不會拍了，他會不會拍可以作為香港有沒有言論自由的標誌。不是寒蟬效應，是直接反言論自由。你犧牲、付代價，一定「自由」，但言論自由講的是免於代價、免於恐懼。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Freedom_of_speech\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FFreedom_of_speech&d=N%2B9SyAXHNe8JODsndO18Bbc9MeEcP%2Bid7GYOBZmoUoI%3D&h=923d3c4d\" target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Freedom_of_speech</a><br />\n<br />\nFreedom of speech is a principle that supports the freedom of an individual or a community to articulate their opinions and ideas without <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>fear</strong></span> of retaliation, censorship, or legal sanction."},{"pid":"dcb0f0cacf42e554eaddd4b72ba663ddee4264d6","tid":1172751,"uid":4739,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T16:44:24.000Z","msg":"法庭之前判案已經話過香港言論自由受限制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad4176dc3e83c9909d21530a9712266cfef756ad","tid":1172751,"uid":228317,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T16:45:31.000Z","msg":"【民陣6.9反惡法